{"tid":1538064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭撤，你會撤？","createTime":"2019-09-04T06:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T06:25:18.000Z","uid":16733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4a2db31602a0ec75621f05ecc15236b282f2aa26","tid":1538064,"uid":16733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:16:56.000Z","msg":"大家諗下<br />\n<br />\n如果當初6月9號晚百萬人遊行之後林鄭就宣佈撤回，仲會有咁多手足被捕、受傷、被射爆眼嗎？<br />\n<br />\n如果今日林鄭話撤你就乖乖地盤屋企繼續做港豬，你對得住呢段期間為香港付出過嘅人嗎？<br />\n<br />\n如果閣下係好易滿足嘅和理非，希望你都唔介意為公義繼續堅持落去，唔好叫香港人袋住先<br />\n<br />\n向銀行借錢唔準時還都要罰錢啦，想還返本金就算？正常人都知無可能。<br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。香港人加油。"},{"pid":"4afdfe8e8945192c1d79205a85526c5c5bbd17b6","tid":1538064,"uid":133663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:19:21.000Z","msg":"撤佢老母啊擁<br />\n切狗撚就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d64978dd855c310ee948a2bc9dff71321c8a22","tid":1538064,"uid":105332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"成立獨立調查委員會呀🤬🤬🤬🤬"},{"pid":"2d84e8747a1b4c2a4731111aa53aa3ec99eef1bd","tid":1538064,"uid":121869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mS3qqGn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmS3qqGn.jpg&h=e0db4b33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地不如整理下殉國手足，然後一世都記住佢地，好嗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532408</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n民族自強 港人自救<br />\n沒有暴徒 只有暴政<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"9256ca5cae91ef8b0ca2773ace0247997f01ab93","tid":1538064,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:24:37.000Z","msg":"撤佢老母，五大訴求呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e1df84f285e3badf36654cde099e0a029647a1","tid":1538064,"uid":266382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:25:18